COACH: Go! Go!

36
00:01:39.642 --> 00:01:42.103
- I see him! Ah!
- PLAYER: Lay it up!

37
00:01:43.521 --> 00:01:45.147
Here. here! Horse!

38
00:01:47.399 --> 00:01:48.234
Ugh!

39
