89
00:04:28.185 --> 00:04:29.478
(chuckling)

90
00:04:29.561 --> 00:04:32.398
Horse? Come on. man.
You've been in there forever!

91
00:04:32.815 --> 00:04:34.125
You sure you're alone in there. pal?

92
00:04:34.149 --> 00:04:35.276
- What's going on?
- Yeah!

93
00:04:35.859 --> 00:04:37.236
