682
00:35:13.821 --> 00:35:15.239
(footsteps receding)

683
00:35:15.322 --> 00:35:17.324
(mysterious music)

684
00:35:33.173 --> 00:35:34.299
REL: Where is everybody?

685
00:35:37.803 --> 00:35:39.555
