1563
01:21:39.270 --> 01:21:41.188
CHRYS: (echoing) No...

1564
01:21:47.945 --> 01:21:49.030
(echoing) Ellie...

1565
01:21:50.072 --> 01:21:51.240
(echoing) Chrys.

1566
01:21:54.535 --> 01:21:55.953
ELLIE: I'm sorry...

1567
01:22:11.052 --> 01:22:11.928
